# Summary
Behavioral cohorts in Amplitude allow users to group individuals based on shared actions within specific time periods, enabling segmentation in charts to analyze how product engagement affects business outcomes, with availability limited to Plus, Growth, and Enterprise plans, and a restriction of five behavioral cohorts for Plus plan organizations.

